<section>
  <h2>Removed &mdash; Use data-effect="ticker"</h2>
  <p>The <code>data-ticker</code> attribute has been removed. The ticker is now part of the <a href="/docs/attributes/data-effect/#ticker">unified effects system</a>.</p>

  <h3>New Syntax</h3>
  <code-block language="html" label="Current ticker usage">{{ '<data value="50000"\n      data-effect="ticker"\n      data-trigger="scroll"\n      style="--vb-ticker-duration: 2000">50,000</data>' | escape }}</code-block>

  <h3>What Changed</h3>
  <table class="props-table">
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Old (removed)</th><th>New</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>data-ticker</code></td><td><code>data-effect="ticker"</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>data-ticker="2000"</code> (duration)</td><td><code>style="--vb-ticker-duration: 2000"</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>data-ticker-start="500"</code></td><td><code>style="--vb-ticker-start: 500"</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>data-ticker-decimals="2"</code></td><td><code>style="--vb-ticker-decimals: 2"</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td>(auto IntersectionObserver)</td><td><code>data-trigger="scroll"</code></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3>Documentation</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/docs/attributes/data-effect/#ticker">data-effect="ticker"</a> &mdash; Full effect documentation with live demos</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/elements/native/data/">data element</a> &mdash; Ticker, number formatting, byte formatting</li>
  </ul>
</section>
